            "id": 6434282,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 超微電腦(SMCI-US)大跌5.02%，報27.62美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>超微電腦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SMCI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SMCI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SMCI-US</a>)截至台北時間27日23:20股價下跌1.46美元，報27.62美元，跌幅5.02%，成交量13,375,312（股），盤中最高價29.49美元、最低價27.61美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.35%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.23%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.34%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-2.02%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>超微電腦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SMCI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SMCI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SMCI-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.82%</li> <li>近 1 月：+30.93%</li> <li>近 3 月：-5.58%</li> <li>近 6 月：-39.78%</li> <li>今年以來：-0.65%</li></ul></section></main>",
